t type, allowing context-aware pseudo-label expansion (e.g., SRE-guided label propagation for rare classes). This creates a closed-loop system where model weaknesses inform agent specialization, and agent debates drive data acquisition. The framework significantly reduces redundant labeling, accelerates convergence, and enhances robustness to domain shifts by ensuring diverse, high-information yield batches. Impact spans autonomous systems and medical imaging, where both structural and semantic anomalies must be captured efficiently without human-in-the-loop oversight.",
